* Kleinert, Hagen, ''Gauge Fields in Condensed Matter'', Vol. II, "STRESSES AND DEFECTS; Differential Geometry, Crystal Melting", pp. 743-1456, World Scientific, Singapore, 1989; Paperback ISBN 9971-5-0210-0 '' （电子版[http://www.physik.fu-berlin.de/~kleinert/kleiner_reb1/contents2.html 在线阅读]）''
* Meyers and Chawla., ''Mechanical Behaviors of Materials.'' Prentice Hall, Inc., 1999, pp. 228-231.
}}

